node.text:
The permanent make-up industry has blessed us in such amazing ways 🥰

This Pay With A Smile event was a day of pure happiness for 100+ Cancer Survivors, where over 35 Phiacademy Artist from around the world come together in one place to donate their time and beautiful art just for one reason and that's to bring a smile into these beautiful warriors ❤ 
Thanks to all Phiacademy Artist who participated and special thans to @andy_browsir 
for his contributions to Pay With A Smile 🙌

#paywithasmile #phiacademyusa #phiacademy #phi #phibrows #brankobabicacademy #microblading #browlove #makeup #beauty #permanentmakeup #cancersurvivor #cancer #blessed #breastcancer #cancersucks #cancerdemama #mexico #usa #america #california

node.text:
Can you imagine to share your business with your mother? They can do it for sure!
Grand Master Diana Hvas and her daughter, master Stephanie Hvas created their beauty fairytale in Denmark.
But it wasn’t always bright...grow up on the edge of society and become successful? Possible!
Watch why the beauty industry is not always for business? How those beautiful ladies become a winning team? How they succeed in a country with the highest taxes and where natural beauty standards are must-have!
Stay tuned with Phi TV!

node.text:
Grand master Ella Sakalauskiene is example that you can do everything, you just need to wish and work hard!
Modern lady who built her career by her own, who made worldwide success but have never forgot her roots! Her life is always in suitcases ready for sharing PhiRemoval magic!
Behind smiley face there is inspirational story which will put tears on your face.

node.text:
She is the best in her job, and he is the best in his! Together they are just PERFECT!
Kerstin Ellmer and Thorsten Kreiling are the most successful couple in PMU. They both have Grand Master titles, but they are simple, funny and unique people.
Watch their story, and realize how curiosity, hard work and passion can change your life!
From elevator contractor to the best Phi contour artists!
From a loved woman and dedicated mother to the most inspiring teacher!
Why the whole world loves their eyeliner and lips? The answer is simple, they are THE BEST.
